0.5.name: wordpress/where-im-going
0.5.description: This plug-in allows you to input your travel destinations and the dates you'll be there, then easily output those dates to your readers. Destinations can be linked to Wordpress posts and pages to direct your readers to your content. Output is fully customizable to show destinations and dates in any format.
